// 用word break i中的矩阵（表示到string的第i个字母最少要用几步(或者能不能到达)），如果步数不是INT_MAX，才进行迭代
// 但这样仍然是糟糕的写法（896ms）

// 未完待续

class Solution {
public:
    vector<string> wordBreak(string s, vector<string>& wordDict) {
        vector<string> ans;
        vector<string> path;
        vector<int> dp(s.size() + 1, INT_MAX);
        if(canWordBreak(s,wordDict,dp)){
            wordBreak(s, wordDict, ans, path, 0, 0, dp);
        }
        return ans;
    }
private:
    void wordBreak(string s, vector<string>& wordDict, vector<string> &ans, vector<string> &path, int pathlen, int beg, vector<int> &dp){
        if(pathlen == s.size()){
            ans.push_back(splitPath(path));
            return;
        }
        if(beg >= s.size()){
            return;
        }
        string tmp;
        for(int i = 0; i < wordDict.size(); ++i){
            if(beg + wordDict[i].size() <= s.size() && dp[beg + wordDict[i].size()] != INT_MAX){
                tmp = s.substr(beg, wordDict[i].size());
                if(tmp == wordDict[i]){
                    path.push_back(wordDict[i]);
                    wordBreak(s, wordDict, ans, path, pathlen+wordDict[i].size(), beg+wordDict[i].size(), dp);
                    path.pop_back();
                    wordBreak(s, wordDict, ans, path, pathlen, beg+1, dp);
                }
            }
        }
    }
    string splitPath(vector<string> path){
        string ret;
        if(path.size() == 0)    return ret;
        ret = path[0];
        for(int i = 1; i < path.size(); ++i){
            ret = ret + " " + path[i];
        }
        return ret;
    }
    bool canWordBreak(string s, vector<string>& wordDict, vector<int>& dp) {
        // 每一格表示，到第i位，最少使用步数
        //vector<int> dp(s.size() + 1, INT_MAX);
        dp[0] = 0;
        string tmp; int wordlen;
        for(int i = 1; i <= s.size(); ++i){
            for(int j = 0; j < wordDict.size(); ++j){
                wordlen = wordDict[j].size();
                if(wordlen <= i){
                    tmp = s.substr(i - wordlen,wordlen);
                    if(tmp == wordDict[j] && dp[i - wordlen] != INT_MAX)
                        dp[i] = min(dp[i],dp[i - wordlen]+1);
                }
            }
        }
        if(dp[s.size()] != INT_MAX)   return true;
        return false;
        
    }
};

// -----------------------------暗中观察10ms左右的解法，都用到Hash----------------------------
// 做了一个非常好的初始化
// dp存了从第i个字母开始所有可能选择的dict长度，因而在dfs的过程中，避免了大量不必要的分支，机智
class Solution {
public:
    vector<string> wordBreak(string s, vector<string>& wordDict) {
        int n = s.size();
        set<int> word_sizes;
        for(auto& word : wordDict)
        {
            word_sizes.insert(word.size());
        }
        unordered_set<string> dict(wordDict.begin(), wordDict.end());
        
        vector<vector<int>> dp(n, vector<int>{});
        
        for(int j = n; j > 0; j--)
        {
            if(j != n && dp[j].empty()) continue;
            for(auto& a : word_sizes)
            {
                if(j - a < 0) break;
                string word_to_search = s.substr(j-a, a);
                if(dict.count(word_to_search) > 0) dp[j-a].push_back(a);
            }
        }
        
        vector<string> ret;
        dfs(ret, s, "", 0, dp);
        return ret;
    }
    
    void dfs(vector<string>& ret, const string& s, string sol, int level, const vector<vector<int>>& dp)
    {
        if(level == s.size())
        {
            ret.push_back(sol);
            return;
        }
        
        for(auto a : dp[level])
        {
            string new_sol = sol;
            if(sol.empty()) new_sol += s.substr(level, a);
            else new_sol += " " + s.substr(level , a);
            dfs(ret, s, new_sol, level+a, dp);
        }
    }
};
